               <p>JAMES ILES CHAFFIN. On the 25th of February I was returning with a friend from Drury-lane Theatre - I was under <placeName id="t18280221-277-crimeloc1467">the Piazza in Covent-garden, near James-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18280221-277-crimeloc1467" type="placeName" value="the Piazza in Covent-garden, near James-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18280221-277-crimeloc1467" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280221-277-off1465 t18280221-277-crimeloc1467"></join>, and had an opera-glass in my right-hand coat pocket (I do not reside in town) - I felt my pocket lighter; an officer came and told me I had been robbed, and produced it. I had not seen the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280221-277-person1556">
                  JOHN 
                  BOSTON
               <interp inst="t18280221-277-person1556" type="surname" value="BOSTON"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18280221-277-person1556" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18280221-277-person1556" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a watchman, in the employ of the Commissioners of Woods and Forests. I was returning home, and saw the prisoner and another go up to this gentleman; the prisoner took the glass out of his pocket - I seized them both, but was obliged to let the other go, as there were a number of boys and girls round; I took the glass from him.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner. He has a spite against me.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18280221-277-verdict1468" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18280221-277-verdict1468" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 11.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18280221-277-punish1469" type="punishmentDescription">
